* [[托比·马圭尔|托比·马圭尔]]饰演{{link-en|彼得·帕克 (山姆·雷米电影系列)|Peter Parker (Sam Raimi film series)|彼得·帕克}}／[[蜘蛛侠|蜘蛛侠]]（{{lang|en|Peter Parker / Spider-Man}}）
: 一名学习成绩优异但社交上无能的纽约高中生，某次被一只基因改造过的蜘蛛咬了一口后他获得类似蜘蛛的超能力，随后将其用于行侠仗义。马圭尔于2000年7月入选出演彼得<ref name="spins" />，山姆·雷米看过《[[总有骄阳|总有骄阳]]》后就将他视为首选<ref name="empire">{{cite news | author = Chris Hewitt, Simon Braund | title = Spider-Man | pages = 58–62 | publisher = ''Empire'' | date = 2002-07}}</ref>。制片公司一开始对请一个看起来五不大三不粗的演员来出演感到有些犹豫<ref name="spins" />，但马圭尔参加试镜时给出了出色的表现。他的片酬在300至400万美元之间，之后的两部续集有望更高<ref name="spins">{{cite news | author=Michael Fleming | author2=Claude Brodesser | url=http://variety.com/2000/film/news/maguire-spins-spider-man-1117784384/ | title=Maguire spins 'Spider-Man' | publisher=''Variety'' | date=2000-07-31 | accessdate=2013-07-14 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302165853/http://variety.com/2000/film/news/maguire-spins-spider-man-1117784384/ | archivedate=2016-03-02 }}</ref>。为了准备，马圭尔接受了[[体能|体能]]、[[瑜伽|瑜伽]]、[[武术|武术]]、攀岩多个方面训练，花了数月的时间改善自己的体格<ref name="friday">{{cite video | title = Friday Night with Jonathan Ross | format = TV | publisher = BBC One |date = 2007-04-27}}</ref>。马圭尔也对蜘蛛进行研究，并与一位钢丝杂技演员一起练习模仿蜘蛛的动作，他还有着专门的饮食安排<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/05/raimi-talks-up-spider-man-but-still-no-goblin | title=Raimi Talks Up ''Spider-Man'', But Still No Goblin | publisher=IGN | date=2000-10-05 | accessdate=2013-07-14 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012042000/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/05/raimi-talks-up-spider-man-but-still-no-goblin | archivedate=2012-10-12 }}</ref>。公司曾考虑过请[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]、[[小弗雷迪·普林兹|小弗雷迪·普林兹]]<ref name="unraveling">{{cite news | author=Ronald Grover | url=http://www.businessweek.com/stories/2002-04-14/unraveling-spider-mans-tangled-web | title=Unraveling Spider-Man's Tangled Web | publisher=''Business Week'' | date=2002-04-15 | accessdate=2013-07-14 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510064647/http://www.businessweek.com/bwdaily/dnflash/apr2002/nf20020415_7441.htm | archivedate=2009-05-10 }}</ref>、[[克里斯·克莱因|克里斯·克莱因]]、[[韦斯·本特利|韦斯·本特利]]和[[希斯·莱杰|希斯·莱杰]]出演<ref name=hughes />。[[詹姆斯·卡梅隆|詹姆斯·卡梅隆]]曾于1995年考虑过请迪卡普里奥来扮演蜘蛛侠<ref>{{cite book | author = David Hughes | title = Comic Book Movies | publisher = Virgin Books | year = 2003 | location = London | page = 233 | isbn = 0-7535-0767-6}}</ref>，雷米对此还对普林兹开玩笑说“（迪卡普里奥）甚至都不会被允许来买票看这部电影”<ref name=hughes>{{cite book | author = David Hughes | title = Comic Book Movies | publisher = Virgin Books | year = 2003 | location = London | pages = 235-241 | isbn = 0-7535-0767-6}}</ref>。此外，[[斯科特·斯比德曼|斯科特·斯比德曼]]、{{link-en|杰伊·罗丹|Jay Rodan}}和[[詹姆斯·弗朗科|詹姆斯·弗朗科]]都参与过主角的试镜<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/19/more-from-the-spider-man-casting-front | title=More From the ''Spider-Man'' Casting Front | publisher=IGN | date=2000-06-19 | accessdate=2013-07-14 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218225107/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/19/more-from-the-spider-man-casting-front | archivedate=2014-02-18 }}</ref>。
